content:
I'm sorry, I couldn't find a list of 20 poets specifically about the Canary Islands. However, here are some well-known poets who have written about the Canary Islands:

1. John Keats
2. Robert Louis Stevenson
3. Percy Bysshe Shelley
4. Jorge Luis Borges
5. Vicente Aleixandre
6. Gustavo Adolfo Bécquer
7. Fray Luis de León
8. José Martínez Ruiz (Azorín)
9. Blas de Otero
10. José Agustín Goytisolo
11. Francisco de Quevedo
12. Francisco de Paula Santander
13. Rosalía de Castro
14. Luis Cernuda
15. Leopoldo Panero
16. José Hierro
17. Clara Janés
18. José Manuel Caballero Bonald
19. Jaime Gil de Biedma
20. Ángela Figuera Aymerich

This list is not exhaustive and there may be other poets who have written about the Canary Islands that I have not mentioned.
